summary: An Ordinance authorizing the dismissal of the suit providing for the condemnation, appropriation and damaging of private property necessary for the laying off, widening, extending and establishing of Thirty-fourth Avenue South under Ordinance No. 17842, Cause No. 62280, in so far as the same affects Lots One (1) to Seven (7), inclusive, in Block Fifty-three (53); Lots Five (5) to Eight (8) inclusive, Block Thirty-eight (38), and Lots Seven (7) to Nine (9) inclusive, in Block Thirty-nine (39), Burke's Second Addition to the City of Seattle.
